  from his collection.</p>

  <p class="footnotetext"><a name="fn7" class="fn" href="#fnref7" id="fn7">7</a> Both the hearing committee and the
  disciplinary board relied on the following cases: <span class="cite">In re: Barry, 01-1722 (La. 10/26/01),
  <a href="2001-10-26_2001-1722.htm">799 So. 2d 479</a></span> (six-month suspension with probation and Ethics School
